HEADWORD: Unfilial
<hw>Un*fil"ial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Unsuitable to a son
or a daughter; undutiful; not becoming a child.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*fil"ial*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

